<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.catholicnews.com/data/stories/cns/0801336.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.catholicnews.com/data/stories/cns/0801336.htm" rel="nofollow">"Social effects of sin greater than ever, says Vatican official=</a><a href="/w/index.php?title=Catholic_News_Sevice&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Catholic News Sevice (page does not exist)">Catholic News Sevice</a>"<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.catholicnews.com/data/stories/cns/0801336.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.catholicnews.com/data/stories/cns/0801336.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.catholicnews.com/data/stories/cns/0801336.htm</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Social+effects+of+sin+greater+than+ever%2C+says+Vatican+official%3D%5B%5BCatholic+News+Sevice%5D%5D&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.catholicnews.com%2Fdata%2Fstories%2Fcns%2F0801336.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Seven_deadly_sins"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.americamagazine.org/blog/entry.cfm?blog_id=2&amp;id=9A0A606B-5056-8960-327C219014498879" class="external text" title="http://www.americamagazine.org/blog/entry.cfm?blog_id=2&amp;id=9A0A606B-5056-8960-327C219014498879" rel="nofollow">"Seven Seven (New) Deadly Sins? Or Not?"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/America_(magazine)" title="America (magazine)">America (magazine)</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.americamagazine.org/blog/entry.cfm?blog_id=2&amp;id=9A0A606B-5056-8960-327C219014498879" class="external free" title="http://www.americamagazine.org/blog/entry.cfm?blog_id=2&amp;id=9A0A606B-5056-8960-327C219014498879" rel="nofollow">http://www.americamagazine.org/blog/entry.cfm?blog_id=2&amp;id=9A0A606B-5056-8960-327C219014498879</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Seven+Seven+%28New%29+Deadly+Sins%3F+Or+Not%3F&amp;rft.atitle=%5B%5BAmerica+%28magazine%29%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.americamagazine.org%2Fblog%2Fentry.cfm%3Fblog_id%3D2%26id%3D9A0A606B-5056-8960-327C219014498879&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Seven_deadly_sins"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
